-- Forty People Die as Flames Engulf Overturned Bus in Northern Israel Fire
-- B y   C a l e v   B e n - D a v i d
-- 2010-12-02T15:17:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-02/forty-people-die-as-flames-engulf-overturned-bus-in-northern-israel-fire.html
A bus overturned during a forest fire
outside the northern Israeli city of Haifa killing about 40
people, Zaka Rescue and Recovery Service spokesman Moti Bukjin
said in a phone interview.  To contact the reporter on this story:
